akka.typed

Class DispatcherFromExecutionContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • akka.typed.DeploymentConfig
      • akka.typed.DispatcherFromExecutionContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DispatcherSelector, java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product

    public final class DispatcherFromExecutionContext
extends DeploymentConfig
implements DispatcherSelector, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    Directly use the given ExecutionContext whenever the actor needs to be run. No attempt will be made to shut down this thread pool, even if it is an instance of ExecutorService.
    See Also:
